loghub.processors

Class VarExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • loghub.Processor
      • loghub.processors.FieldsProcessor
        • loghub.processors.VarExtractor

  • public class VarExtractor
extends FieldsProcessor
    This transformer parse a field using a regex that extract name and value. The regex must contains two named group name and value. The field is parsed until exhaustion. The unmatched content will stay in the field unless everything match, in this case, the field is removed.

    The default parser is "(?<name>\p{Alnum}+)\p{Space}?[=:]\p{Space}?(?<value>[^;,:]+)[;,:]?" and should match most common case

    Author:
    Fabrice Bacchella
